soldebug uses Foundry's internal crates as dependencies (via git submodule at
lib/foundry/) for EVM execution, trace collection, source mapping, contract
identification, and Solidity compilation. These crates include but are not
limited to: foundry-evm, foundry-evm-core, foundry-evm-traces, foundry-config,
foundry-common, and foundry-compilers.

